#: includes/class-acp-feed.php:691
msgid "Missing brand (submitted without it)"
msgstr "Marque manquante (envoyés sans)"

#: includes/class-acp-feed.php:691
msgid "These rows enter the feed without the brand field; OpenAI may reject them. Assign a brand (WooCommerce Brands taxonomy or a brand attribute) to make them fully conformant."
msgstr "Ces lignes entrent dans le flux sans le champ marque ; OpenAI peut les rejeter. Attribuez une marque (taxonomie Marques de WooCommerce ou attribut de marque) pour les rendre pleinement conformes."

#: includes/class-acp-feed.php:692
msgid "Missing primary image"
msgstr "Image principale manquante"

#: includes/class-acp-feed.php:692
msgid "Set a featured image in the product editor."
